<item>
            <title>[DERBY-4902] Encoding problem in output from plan exporter</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-4902</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If I execute a query with non-ASCII characters in it, the output from the plan exporter tool is garbled.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Example query: select * from bl&#229;b&#230;r&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The HTML output looks like this in the browser: Query: select * from bl&#195;&#165;b&#195;&#166;r&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Similar problem with XML: &amp;lt;statement&amp;gt;select * from bl&#195;&#165;b&#195;&#166;r&amp;lt;/statement&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12479939">DERBY-4902</key>
            <summary>Encoding problem in output from plan exporter</summary>
